snippet.title: MY NEW FAVOURITE FOOTBALL TEAM!!!! Partick Thistle v Dunfermline, Scottish Cup
snippet.description:
I FINALLY saw Partick Thistle play at Firhill Stadium in Glasgow. 

My Thistle merch: https://www.ebay.co.uk/itm/Partick-Thistle-Firhill-Stadium-Canvas-30-x-20-cm-NEW/154703646815

The Scottish Cup is in full swing this weekend in Scotland and I saw Dunfermline take on Partick Thistle at Firhill on a cold Friday night in Maryhill. 

The atmosphere was incredible and the Partick Thistle fans sang all game in the John Lambie stand!

Scott Tiffoney was the star of the show for me as Thistle progressed to the next round after a 1-0 win! MON THE JAGS!!!

My merch:
https://www.ebay.co.uk/usr/samno-250643

#Football #PartickThistle #Scotland
